{"tid":1428803,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"李純恩：瑞士銀行也使壞了","createTime":"2019-08-07T11:04:46.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-07T14:38:53.000Z","uid":141151,"like":28,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"e82b222199055479f7ff2332eb44b6a87e10a409","tid":1428803,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T11:04:46.000Z","msg":"李純恩：瑞士銀行也使壞了<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://topick.hket.com/article/2420408/%E6%9D%8E%E7%B4%94%E6%81%A9%EF%BC%9A%E7%91%9E%E5%A3%AB%E9%8A%80%E8%A1%8C%E4%B9%9F%E4%BD%BF%E5%A3%9E%E4%BA%86\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftopick.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2420408%2F%25E6%259D%258E%25E7%25B4%2594%25E6%2581%25A9%25EF%25BC%259A%25E7%2591%259E%25E5%25A3%25AB%25E9%258A%2580%25E8%25A1%258C%25E4%25B9%259F%25E4%25BD%25BF%25E5%25A3%259E%25E4%25BA%2586&d=%2BDaDB54%2FKEfuO7Vsi8VjQ3fp3ZHOIdf2SFoQnphXrww%3D&h=b186c2fa\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://topick.hket.com/article/2420408/%E6%9D%8E%E7%B4%94%E6%81%A9%EF%BC%9A%E7%91%9E%E5%A3%AB%E9%8A%80%E8%A1%8C%E4%B9%9F%E4%BD%BF%E5%A3%9E%E4%BA%86</a><br />\n<br />\n瑞士銀行承諾將自動向其他國家--當然以美國為首--提供外國人帳戶的詳細資料，想不到對這個決定反應最大的是中國人。<br />\n<br />\n據說在外國記者會上被問到這件事的時候，中國外交部發言人華春瑩回答：「我們注意到瑞士的新動向，我們嚴肅敦促瑞方以對世界和平負責，對人類安定團結負責和尊重他人財產隱私的態度，謹言慎行，充分認識公開客戶財產信息可能導致的嚴重後果。」<br />\n<br />\n以上這段是網上消息，網上消息真假難辨，我當然希望這一段只是網民惡作劇的假消息，但萬一是真的，那也不出奇，因為神奇的國度，像惡作劇一樣的現實情況又實在太多。<br />\n<br />\n結果內地媒體證實，這則在中國社交媒體廣泛流傳的「所謂中國外交部回應」的舊聞，的確是假新聞。<br />\n<br />\n不過，如果從一個正面積極的角度去看，瑞士銀行肯向外國國家機構透露客戶資料，對中國也不是壞事，中國不是大力肅貪嗎？如今存在瑞士銀行裏的中國客戶存款，頭一百位中國客戶加起來的總數據說高達七萬八千億元人民幣，這麼大一筆數字裏面，能為肅貪提供多大的信息量？可以做多大文章出來？<br />\n<br />\n除非，這些錢是不能做文章的。"},{"pid":"9b278b0caa5bee21095f21fd0d6972ded910d8f7","tid":1428803,"uid":470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T11:05:25.000Z","msg":"感冒童<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"92eb03ef032a53715012f6a92279ac1009e3b05e","tid":1428803,"uid":36378,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T11:06:38.000Z","msg":"亮劍<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a5acfa0fa5ff893d79fdc7aa3a28d311dd42da5","tid":1428803,"uid":272569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T13:58:06.000Z","msg":"推到瑞銀公開狗官資料"},{"pid":"44e8119d1c564c12f79b0f426eb45e416f6ac900","tid":1428803,"uid":272569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T14:12:12.000Z","msg":"推到知點攪先公開"},{"pid":"50e7d46f3b13ecd4ac0a89afda692aba2a997118","tid":1428803,"uid":41458,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T14:13:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"062ff699e28ae696091e26ca24e45a1dc1fd7484","tid":1428803,"uid":142854,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T14:13:45.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">[急] 全港十八區出現武器庫丶軍火原材料</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n汽油彈（英語：Molotov Cocktail，俄語：Кокте́йль Мо́лотова，意為「莫洛托夫雞尾酒」），又稱燃燒彈，是游擊隊等非正規部隊，<ins><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">以及街頭暴亂群眾的常用武器，有些罪犯也會以它來縱火。</span></strong></span></ins>軍方亦有採用，不同於制式武器凝固汽油彈。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">燃燒瓶的主要構造為：玻璃瓶，</span></span><del><span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">瓶內裝有半滿的易燃液體，例如三分之二的汽油與三分之一的油混合而成的液體或酒精（甲醇或乙醇）； 瓶口以軟木塞或塑膠、橡膠、電線膠帶、牛皮膠帶等不透氣塞堵住；瓶口上紮上布塊作引。 使用之前把布塊沾透易燃液體，燃點布塊後把瓶拋出。玻璃瓶撞擊目標破裂，易燃液體傾倒在目標之上，被火點著燃燒，可造成一定的阻絕及殺傷能力。<br />\n<br />\n蘇聯曾經製造制式汽油彈，外面裝有兩根密封有濃硫酸的玻璃管。投擲碰碎之後靠化學反應產生的熱量點燃油料，從而節省了點火步驟。<br />\n<br />\n燃燒瓶的原理跟正規軍隊使用的燃燒彈基本相同；兩者都是以汽油混合使汽油變稠的物料。<br />\n<br />\n另外也有人使用塑膠袋裝汽油，因為塑膠袋可以承載著一定容量的液體。</span></del><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://gia.info.gov.hk/general/201404/06/P201404040808_photo_1067314.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fgia.info.gov.hk%2Fgeneral%2F201404%2F06%2FP201404040808_photo_1067314.JPG&h=2cfe9af1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n18區陸續出現多種以綠色標誌的可疑軍火庫<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.enb.gov.hk/sites/default/files/zh-hant/node5045/4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.enb.gov.hk%2Fsites%2Fdefault%2Ffiles%2Fzh-hant%2Fnode5045%2F4.jpg&h=eac93a3e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n不知名人士正在提取疑似軍火<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20130401/large/01ls3p2a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20130401%2Flarge%2F01ls3p2a.jpg&h=74db3026&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://gia.info.gov.hk/general/201407/20/P201407180904_photo_1071737.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fgia.info.gov.hk%2Fgeneral%2F201407%2F20%2FP201407180904_photo_1071737.JPG&h=419e2799&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n亦有熱心人士幫忙抽走疑似軍火<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.epd.gov.hk/epd/sites/default/files/epd/tc_chi/environmentinhk/waste/eco_responsibility/files/Poster_private1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.epd.gov.hk%2Fepd%2Fsites%2Fdefault%2Ffiles%2Fepd%2Ftc_chi%2Fenvironmentinhk%2Fwaste%2Feco_responsibility%2Ffiles%2FPoster_private1.jpg&h=5b1cffb0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n可疑單張來源不明<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">認同請分享 同意請按讚 好人一生平安 <br />\ntag#香港加油!#和平!</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"84b60fa6f1a812b0ebcab2169b9e110f2e7b8b45","tid":1428803,"uid":69841,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T14:14:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db3aa7394b43f3607c3c740faced521a7fea7e6a","tid":1428803,"uid":150935,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T14:15:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"df57c4423b6b50883bb15cc8e7ffa38ecf3c1a2f","tid":1428803,"uid":25468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T14:15:47.000Z","msg":"幾年前新聞"},{"pid":"35fc4e003d4174d9cfaa6790fa352c37f7388961","tid":1428803,"uid":263806,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T14:37:07.000Z","msg":"習大大係到拎返都夠玩一段時間<br />\n推到習大大支持瑞士銀行公開資料"},{"pid":"b507f60a3acac0ade4fa25d047e400b977001376","tid":1428803,"uid":272569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"df57c4423b6b50883bb15cc8e7ffa38ecf3c1a2f","tid":1428803,"uid":25468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T14:15:47.000Z","msg":"幾年前新聞"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T14:38:53.000Z","msg":"三年前，不過唔知點解又講<br />\n<br />\n推到知點攪先公開"}]}